    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This unit is paired with a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission, offering crisp gear synchronization and mechanical engagement. Performance is bolstered by a factory-spec limited-slip differential, ensuring precise torque distribution across the rear axle. Critical preventative maintenance is documented: the VANOS system has been overhauled with upgraded seals, and the rod bearings have been replaced to ensure long-term reciprocating assembly health. Furthermore, the rear subframe has been reinforced to mitigate common chassis fatigue. While the exterior shows minor patina, the suspension geometry remains true, and the powertrain pulls hard through the entire 8,000 RPM sweep. Ideal for the purist who values mechanical pedigree over concours-level aesthetics.",
